<p><b>Scalphunter</b> (<b>John Greycrow</b>) is a fictional <a href="/wiki/Mutant_(Marvel_Comics)" title="Mutant (Marvel Comics)">mutant</a> villain character appearing in <a href="/wiki/American_comic_book" title="American comic book">American comic books</a> published by <a href="/wiki/Marvel_Comics" title="Marvel Comics">Marvel Comics</a>. His first appearance was in <i><a href="/wiki/Uncanny_X-Men" title="Uncanny X-Men">Uncanny X-Men</a></i> #210. This character was created by <a href="/wiki/Chris_Claremont" title="Chris Claremont">Chris Claremont</a>, <a href="/wiki/John_Romita_Jr." title="John Romita Jr.">John Romita Jr.</a> and <a href="/wiki/Dan_Green_(artist)" title="Dan Green (artist)">Dan Green</a>.
</p>
